<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ingredient" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ingredient,</orth> something entering into a compound: <cit><quote>the abhorred i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 43</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the i. is a devil,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.311" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 311</bibl></cit> (Qq <emph>ingredience</emph>). In <bibl n="shak. mac 1.7.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 7, 11</bibl> and <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 34</bibl> O. Edd. <emph>ingredience.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>